al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該禁區外，跟住辛坦拿又係禁區外射展翅射球但都俾林源三撲到，所以證明唔到沙里拿斯勁過林源三，但之後係禁區內仲要窄角度俾戴志偉二段倒掛入撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640b09efdd8adc2ec37932c8c032830b1b5ff6ad","tid":177722,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">足球風雲真係好好睇！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有邊個估到個作者竟然係女人丫，咁先勁&hellip;"},{"pid":"a4ef6bf603f5762fc78868ce484bc0ecc49180d5","tid":177722,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"林源三好似都覺得梅拿先係最top<br />\n<br />\n梅拿 &gt; 源三 &gt; 巴西佬 &gt; 希林狄 &gt; 健威 &gt; 森崎 &gt; 中西"},{"pid":"ffaf6e82a37cec9eb80a29bf77ec67693726c122","tid":177722,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>閃電十一人 圓堂守</blockquote><br />\n呢套野D人物根本係屌打所有動漫人物咁滯<br />\n足球小將只係超現實佢地直情玩埋超能力點會夠佢地玩</blockquote><br />\n上埋太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec99750d836156de1473c6311eeb24ddb221275","tid":177722,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如講下林源三定健威勁d 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n守龍黎講源三，前鋒黎講可能健威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97540c1020d9f4123d914a302b0296dd52a6e2b","tid":177722,"uid":54354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林源三好似都覺得梅拿先係最top<br />\n<br />\n梅拿 &gt; 源三 &gt; 巴西佬 &gt; 希林狄 &gt; 健威 &gt; 森崎 &gt; 中西</blockquote><br />\n無左墨西哥佬既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e07ba19fcacb7089f27e4d6500aae67aaa8ec47","tid":177722,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply