lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學後唔計泰國果場<br />\n基本上個波射得中龍都有波入<br />\n但佢竟然仲留得低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最初志水隊個龍, 都應該好過森崎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08d0f7e7d448ea4768ae0648cd682f21116ebb8","tid":177722,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>森崎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學後唔計泰國果場<br />\n基本上個波射得中龍都有波入<br />\n但佢竟然仲留得低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最初志水隊個龍, 都應該好過森崎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗成隊日本隊除左樑仔應該冇人入唔到森崎波"},{"pid":"fac443d258bd59e5ac7b30ae95ab66c7453c5471","tid":177722,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>足球騎士李秋俊</blockquote><br />\n漫畫睇到佢代表返泡菜好型,點知之後個apps唔知做乜收左皮,我都無睇落去<br />\n想問係咪仲畫緊?"},{"pid":"584b195d193065ac29790cc6f9b80266db718929","tid":177722,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"其實點解歐陽健威叫歐陽健威？"},{"pid":"832a9d9931763abdfa493ff6a458d210ab93a1f7","tid":177722,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解歐陽健威叫歐陽健威？</blockquote><br />\n好多喎<br />\n戴翅偉 麥泰來 林源三 <br />\n<br />\n反而奇怪點解當時小志強姓小既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a7ca2aaa04762ee0b45063b7350ef0aaf07acc","tid":177722,"uid":22706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>森崎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學後唔計泰國果場<br />\n基本上個波射得中龍都有波入<br />\n但佢竟然仲留得低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最初志水隊個龍, 都應該好過森崎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=